&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Making a career and being true to yourself with Lena Pejgan Nyström (Adobo &amp; Avocados #10)</title><link>https://nicolevanderhoeven.github.io/blog/20230728-ana10-making-a-career-and-being-true-to-yourself/</link><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jul 2023 21:25:02 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://nicolevanderhoeven.github.io/blog/20230728-ana10-making-a-career-and-being-true-to-yourself/</guid><description>&lt;p>My friend &lt;a href="https://testingwithmarie.com">Marie Cruz&lt;/a> and I speak to Lena Pejgan Nyström, the author and creator of &lt;a href="https://pejgan.se/WHRI.htm">Would Heu-risk it?&lt;/a> cards and book about various topics!&lt;/p>
